  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dca.\u0d86\u0dbb\u0dca. \u0dc3\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dda\u0dad\u0dba\u0dda \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dc2\u0dab\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Q.R. A test of the symbol from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Q.R. Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, Minister of Power and Energy, said this afternoon (19) that fuel will be dispensed to the symbol and the last digit of the vehicle's registration number at several locations in Colombo from tomorrow (21st) to 24th.",
        "The minister further said that the program will not be implemented nationwide from tomorrow (21st) and will be implemented nationwide from next 25th.",
        "Q.R. The minister said that the number of people registered in the symbol is 2 million as of this afternoon and the dates on which fuel can be obtained have been changed according to the last digit of the vehicle's registration number.",
        "If the last digit of the vehicle registration number is 0, 1 and 2, Tuesday and Saturday, if 3, 4 and 5 are Thursday and Sunday, and if 6, 7, 8 and 9 are Monday, Wednesday and Friday, the days are reserved for getting fuel."
      ],
